### ========== Update Assets ==========

### AS3-1. 更新資產 - 調整持有數量（加碼）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/{{assetId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "2330.TW",
  "name": "台積電",
  "quantity": 150,
  "costPrice": 620,
  "note": "加碼買入，平均成本提高"
}

### AS3-2. 更新資產 - 部分賣出
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/{{assetId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "CRYPTO",
  "symbol": "BTC",
  "name": "比特幣",
  "quantity": 0.3,
  "costPrice": 1200000,
  "note": "部分獲利了結"
}

### ========== Delete Assets ==========

### AS4-1. 刪除資產（全部賣出清倉）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/{{assetId}}

### ========== Error Tests ==========

### AS5-1. 測試建立資產 - 帳戶不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "TEST",
  "name": "測試",
  "quantity": 1,
  "costPrice": 100
}
# 預期：404 Not Found

### AS5-2. 測試建立資產 - 數量為負數
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "TEST",
  "name": "測試",
  "quantity": -10,
  "costPrice": 100
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request，數量必須大於 0

### AS5-3. 測試建立資產 - 成本價為 0
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "TEST",
  "name": "測試",
  "quantity": 10,
  "costPrice": 0
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request，成本價必須大於 0

### AS5-4. 測試建立資產 - 重複的代號
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "2330.TW",
  "name": "台積電",
  "quantity": 10,
  "costPrice": 600
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request，已有相同代號的資產

### AS5-5. 測試查詢不存在的資產
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
# 預期：404 Not Found


###############################################################################
# 整合測試情境 - 投資帳戶完整流程
###############################################################################

### ========== 情境：建立投資帳戶並新增持倉 ==========

### IS1-1. 先建立投資帳戶
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "富邦證券",
  "type": "INVESTMENT",
  "initialBalance": 0,
  "description": "股票投資專用帳戶"
}
# 複製回應的 id，更新上方的 @investmentAccountId

### IS1-2. 新增第一筆資產 - 台積電
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "STOCK",
  "symbol": "2330.TW",
  "name": "台積電",
  "quantity": 100,
  "costPrice": 600
}

### IS1-3. 新增第二筆資產 - 比特幣
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "accountId": "{{investmentAccountId}}",
  "type": "CRYPTO",
  "symbol": "BTC",
  "name": "比特幣",
  "quantity": 0.5,
  "costPrice": 1200000
}

### IS1-4. 查看帳戶資訊（應該顯示總市值）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{investmentAccountId}}
# currentBalance 應該等於所有資產的市值加總

### IS1-5. 查看帳戶的所有資產
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/account/{{investmentAccountId}}
# 應該顯示：台積電 100股、比特幣 0.5個
# 每筆都有 marketValue（市值）、profitLoss（損益）等計算欄位

### ========== 情境：模擬價格變動（Phase 4 會自動化）==========

### IS2-1. 手動更新台積電當前價格（模擬漲價）
# Phase 4 會改用 API 自動更新，現在先手動測試
